item.title: Subjecting myself to a potential failure
item.description: I am at a point now where I do not officially have a job. The work I do right now demands a better grasp on many programming fundamentals and on a programming language other than Python - preferably JVM based. I am not a very good programmer or exceptionally intelligent. So I have decided to invest a huge deal of time and effort to learn what I should have learned ages ago.
